vity. Erath/Delcambre Community Care Clinic now open 7-5 Monday-Friday (November 14, 2016) -- The Erath /Delcambre Community Care Clinic is now open 7:00-5:00 Monday-Friday which includes the lunch hour. Hospital Engagement Network Award (December 3, 2014) -- As a result of our commitment to quality and patient safety, Abbeville General has been awarded for providing care that is safer, patient-center and more efficient. Levy Cancer Foundation (December 23, 2013) -- To honor the
