WellSpot by Louisiana Health Department Louisiana is
internationally renowned for its music, culture, cuisine and celebrations held
throughout the state each year. Louisiana is also well known for its unhealthy
lifestyle choices that cause our residents to lead the nation in statistics for
obesity, diabetes, heart disease, stroke and other potentially preventable
chronic diseases. Improving our wellbeing, though, doesn\x92t have to mean giving
up our favorite things like good food, great music and legendary festivals.
