calculated by top patient safety experts, peer-reviewed, fully transparent and
free to the public. For the first time, the Hospital Safety Score includes five
measures of patient-reported experience with the hospital as well as two of the
most common infections, C.diff and MRSA. To see Abbeville General Hospital\x92s full score, and to access
